## What Was Fixed in This Session

### Security
- SSL rejectUnauthorized false→true (then reverted with env-var escape hatch for Supabase CA)
- Security headers: X-Frame-Options, CSP, X-Content-Type-Options, Referrer-Policy, etc.
- CORS wildcard → settings.app_url in Python AI service
- Rate limiting on 6 endpoints:
  - POST /api/sessions: 10/hr
  - POST /api/sessions/[id]/submit: 5/hr
  - GET /api/map/personalized: 20/min
  - POST /api/reflections: 30/hr
  - POST /api/activities: 30/hr
  - GET /api/counselor/students/[id]/meeting-prep: 10/hr
- Embedding array validated (1024-dim floats, all finite) before raw SQL
- Input validation on reflections, onboarding, notifications routes

### Bug Fixes
- BUG-1: EMBED_PROFILE QStash job type unhandled → implemented with Voyage AI + Redis cache
- BUG-2: pgvector raw SQL ran with unvalidated AI output → validated first
- BUG-4: completedCount counted started sessions → fixed to count completedAt NOT NULL
- BUG-5: weekKey used Math.ceil(date/7) → replaced with ISO 8601 getISOWeekKey() (UTC-based)
- Synthesis idempotency: signalProfile.create → upsert in both submit route + QStash handler
- Duplicate reflection create race condition (creatingRef Set guard)
- SessionWizard step count hardcoded "5" → dynamic STEP_LABELS.length
- PulseCheckStep didn't check response.ok before advancing
- TemplateManager delete/toggle didn't check response.ok

### API Error Handling (all 33 routes)
- AuthError class with typed 401/403 status in lib/auth.ts
- apiError() helper — returns 401 for unauth, 403 for forbidden, 500 for server errors
- Previously all errors returned 400

### Privacy
- shareSignals toggle → fans out to all 4 DB fields atomically
- shareSummary → new DB field, persists immediately on toggle change
- Privacy settings fetched from DB on entering step 5 (not initialized to defaults)
- Privacy reset also clears shareSummary
- Counselor summary + meeting-prep routes respect shareSummary (compressedSummary filtered)

### Maintainability
- COOLDOWN_DAYS: 4 files → single lib/constants.ts
- getISOWeekKey: inline in qstash → lib/utils.ts (also fixed UTC timezone bug)
- withShareSignals: lib/privacy-utils.ts
- parsePrompts called 3×/render → 1×
- synthesize.ts: type-safe content blocks, JSON parse error handling, code fence stripping

